    <title type="html"><![CDATA[GAZEBOを使ってみよう ! (Gazebo 構造編)]]></title>
    <link href="http://cir-kit.github.io/blog/2015/01/31/gazebo-architecture/"/>
    <updated>2015-01-31T18:21:33+09:00</updated>
